<br>
He referred to it as &quot;a word that warriors use,&quot; so I assume he was playing a warrior. And true, in the pure game mechanics sense, all a warrior has to do between battles is sit, but we're not talking game mechanics, we're talking about RP. And RP-wise, a warrior might indeed have a lot to do between fights. Cleaning blood off of weapons, tightening buckles, checking gear, generally making sure he's ready to leap into combat again. Or even just mentally steeling himself for the upcoming battle.<br>
