I usually just call it The Spirit. Such as, &quot;Are you in need of The Spirit, friend?&quot; and the usual reply is a hearty &quot;Yes!&quot;.  Everyone I've ever said this too has always known exactly what I'm talking about. <br>
<br>
Interestingly enough, I don't get too many requests for SoW, hardly any at all really. One of my favorite people to spend time with in Norrath is a Barb Shaman, he's the one that gets all the requests, almost every time. The only thing I can figure is that people assume since I'm a druid that I'm sick of the requests so they automatically ask the shaman.<br>
